headline: Snap-on (SNA) Valuation Check After Earnings Beat Dividend Hike And Buybacks
summary: Why Snap-on’s latest earnings and dividend move matter for shareholders Snap-on (SNA) just paired better-than-expected quarterly results with a higher dividend and ongoing buybacks, a combination that puts its cash generation and capital returns in sharper focus for current and prospective shareholders.
